Joel Wilkinson, 3, has  Duchenne Muscular Dystrophy - a disease that will cause his muscles to slowly waste away, leaving him unable to walk . 
 He will eventually need a wheelchair  and has a life expectancy of just 20 . 
 His  sister Phoebe, 5, adores him and looks after him at home and school . 
 Family are now trying to make his short life is as full of joy as possible . 
 